Syntax: BROADCAST <USERS|ANONYMOUS|OPERS> <message>
   
Broadcast sends a message to all connected users or opers, depending
on the first parameter. USERS sends to all users, stating which oper
issued the broadcast, ANONYMOUS does the same, but hides the oper.
OPERS sends a message to all online opers, which is users that have
umode +o or are currently authed and have OPER ON.

Only oper with access +a or higher can send anonymous broadcast.
    
